1. Create a book (May use a template) 
2. On existing book create multiple accounts, divide them into groups with names corresponding to the departments.
3. On the Bkper Bank Connection page connect the employees Expensify credit cards. Now the every transactions made is recorded into Bkper book.
4. Set up #hashtags to organize common types of transactions. 
5. With the aim of retrieving expense reports Bkper add-on should be installed, now the transactions/accounts/groups/balances might be fetched to Google Sheets.
